Keep Spider-Man with Disney and the MCU

   This petition made change with 160,255 supporters!
     __________________________________________________________________

   Nate Phillips (of the Journey Into Comics Network) started this
   petition to Disney and 3 others

   After the news today that Sony walked away from their deal with Disney,
   I cannot in good faith stand by while Spider-man and his fans around
   the world become collateral damage. Spider-man in the MCU has brought
   some of the best moments in modern cinema history. SONY you must let go
   of this property or renegotiate with Disney to keep all of the fans
   happy.
   Please join me in standing against Sony who I'll be boycotting until
   this matter is properly resolved. Share this petition and let's make
   our voices heard!

   www.journeyintocomics.com
   #BoycottSony #SaveSpidermanFromSony
