SAVE THE OA, RENEW THE OA FOR SEASON 3

   0 pessoa já assinou. Ajude a chegar a 150.000!
   Dana Green
   Dana Green assinou este abaixo-assinado…
     __________________________________________________________________

   Rafael Ivan criou este abaixo-assinado para pressionar Renew The OA for
   season 3 (The OA part 3)

   "The OA" has just been cancelled by Netflix on August 5th: the exact
   date for which its online fanbase had planned an online #RenewTheOA
   campaign, requesting for Netflix to renew it for at least a third
   season.

   The Netflix Original series ran for two seasons with a total of 16
   episodes. The show has received great critical acclaim, also reaching
   an 80+ score on Rotten Tomatoes for both seasons. During its run the OA
   has generated a large and dedicated fanbase and what some might call a
   cult following online; a subreddit with over 40,000 subscribers,
   countless theories, fan-video's, fan-art, flashmobs and much more.

   To all of its fans around the world The OA means way more than any of
   the Netflix executives blindly following the numbers could ever
   understand.

   The series was initially planned for a 5 season run with Netflix and
   for the reasons stated above we feel it needs to be given justice in
   the form of a renewal or a final conclusion. The creators Brit Marling
   and Zal Batmanglij deserve to continue their beautiful story, be it on
   Netflix or through another service that is willing to pick it up.

   Please sign and share this petition, use the hashtags #RenewTheOA
   #SaveTheOA and show everyone what The OA means to us!

   Got any ideas how to spread the word? Wanna help spread the word? We
   can talk about how to save the oa not just by talking with netflix
   (which doesn’t help) or with petitions but using billboards, printed
   images, strikes. Dm me on instagram: Ivan.Rafael12

   IDEAS HOW TO SAVE THE OA

   - Sign this petition

   - Cancel your subscription on netflix and tell them the reason was
   because they cancelled The OA

   - Go to Netflix and ask for Shows/Movies and write down The OA Part 3,4
   and 5.

   Let’s show Netflix that we are the strongest fanbase!

   RENEW THE OA!  SAVE THE OA!
